QuestData.Title: Trophies of Gammoth
QuestData.Description: We cannot take all of the credit for this Horde victory, $n. It was you who risked your life to test the bloodspore and it was you who ultimately put an end to Gammothra.$B$BHonor us by returning to Warsong Hold and presenting the head of Gammothra to Lord Hellscream.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Head of Gammothra to Garrosh Hellscream in Warsong Hold.
QuestData.RewardText: <Hellscream picks up the head of Gammothra with one arm and spits in its face.>$B$BThey will learn, $n... They will all learn. The Horde is not to be trifled with...
